e>鬼唔知阿媽係女人，鬼唔知租不如買，咁如果唔租真係買，邊度有錢黎一筆首期，租只要有份工返緊就得</blockquote><br />\n花都唔使廿年前 十年前都係百零萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2115979475274b7e6d108b2c4f5f751d8bb69347","tid":183134,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>頭上個巴打租廿年樓比人笑<br />\n但係度話買樓又比人恥笑接人火棒<br />\n又話之後樓市大跌要比銀行追差價要跳樓<br />\n<br />\n真係唔知點做先岩連登仔心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n租俾人話on9仔幫人供樓<br />\n買樓俾人屌奴隸接火棒，淨係識買樓<br />\n真係頂唔順索性搬上大陸，俾人笑支那狗<br />\n唔上大陸搵夠直情移民，就屌一走了之，去第二個國家做蝗蟲<br />\n連登仔到底想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買樓租比人更加唔洗講 應該比人屌到散左"},{"pid":"666008c4188b40ee30aaadba1f6f743a2ba9a867","tid":183134,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"單親家庭老母個陣無首期錢，入息又過左公屋，<br />\n如果沙士個陣我出黎做緊野應該就買到，可惜個陣我重係中學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b04668ae634098e2e4bfd65a1f0a20cfc68be9","tid":183134,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>住左花都就黎二十年，租緊兩房單位，最近業主話要賣，我屌你老母又要搬<br />\n呢啲二十年樓齡、打風又漏水嘅北區單位都賣到4百幾萬真係痴L線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n租二十年都唔買😱😱</blockquote><br />\n大佬<br />\n<br />\n有人幫我供20年供斷仲唔賣咩<br />\n樓主都識講漏水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n